    "body": "For those reading this in future, we currently have no plans to update the sdk to v6 as this is a major breaking change and we don't want the SDK to be tightly coupled to a specific library like this. This library causes issues for viem users as well.\r\n\r\nWe instead we will be looking into building this functionality into libraries as extensions.  E.g. [viem's decorators](https://viem.sh/docs/clients/custom.html#build-your-own-client) or [web3.js plugins](https://docs.web3js.org/guides/web3_plugin_guide/) or ethers.js plugins.",
